Text: RE QuotesPST no Problem Original Message From Mckay Jonathan SMTPJonathan NRONcom Sent Monday December PM To Mckay Brad Brawner Sandra F Subject Quotes Thank you very much for your work so far gathering market data In an effort to consolidate our requests I have started to include the gulf coast market points This should help limit our random inquiries about different locations and allow everyone to focus on their current business responsibilities Your continued help each night is still needed in verifying the markets during our restructuring time Thank you Best Regards Jon Quotesxls PS If I have missed any locations please advise This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you File Quotesxls
